schools.name: Southern School of Energy and Sustainability

data.description: Spacious and open one level living in premier 55+ community! ASSUMABLE  loan @ 2.5%!  Large kitchen with upgraded light cabinets and granite, breakfast nook overlooking front gardens and separate dining area for entertaining. Gorgeous year round glassed sunroom off large great room!  Large front office. Guest powder room. Spacious primary suite with dual vanity bath, step in shower, separate vanity area and large WIC.  Second primary / guest room with large ensuite bath, WIC.  Oversized garage with ample space for workshop, golf cart or storage. Solar panels for energy efficiency.  Enjoy resort style clubhouse, pools, fitness, pickleball and tennis courts. Year round events, club, fun!  Tangerly Oak model.
